  ('manus_ai_2026_05_03', 'Canadian scholarships and fellowships for developing country students', 'Emerging Leaders in the Americas Program (ELAP)', 'Government of Canada (Global Affairs Canada)', 'Canada', 'https://www.educanada.ca/scholarships-bourses/can/institutions/elap-pfla.aspx?lang=eng', 'tuition_only', '$7,200 for college/undergraduate/graduate students for a minimum of four months or one academic term; $9,700 for graduate students for five to six months of study or research. Covers airfare, health insurance, living expenses, and ground transportation. Tuition fees must be waived by Canadian institutions.', 7200.0, ARRAY['phd','master','bachelor']::text[], NULL, ARRAY['Belize','Bolivia','Brazil','Chile','Colombia','Costa Rica','Cuba','Dominica','Dominican Republic','Ecuador','El Salvador','Guatemala','Guyana','Haiti','Honduras','Jamaica','Mexico','Nicaragua','Panama','Paraguay','Peru','Suriname','Uruguay','Venezuela']::text[], 'Latin America and the Caribbean (Antigua and Barbuda, Bahamas, Barbados, Belize, Bermuda, Bolivia, Brazil, Chile, Colombia, Costa Rica, Cuba, Dominica, Dominican Republic, Ecuador, El Salvador, Grenada, Guatemala, Guyana, Haiti, Honduras, Jamaica, Mexico, Nicaragua, Panama, Paraguay, Peru, Saint Kitts and Nevis, Saint Lucia, Saint Vincent and the Grenadines, Suriname, Trinidad and Tobago, Uruguay, Venezuela).', 'Citizens of eligible countries, enrolled full-time at a post-secondary institution in an eligible country, paying tuition to that institution, not holding Canadian citizenship/PR, not already receiving GAC or federal granting agency funding, not already enrolled in a Canadian degree program. Canadian institutions apply on behalf of candidates.', '2026-03-31'::date, 'fixed', NULL, NULL, 'Government of Canada (Global Affairs Canada)', 'College, undergraduate, and graduate (Master''s and PhD) for short-term study or research.', 'Latin America and the Caribbean (Antigua and Barbuda, Bahamas, Barbados, Belize, Bermuda, Bolivia, B