  ('manus_ai_2026_05_03', 'Canadian scholarships and fellowships for developing country students', 'Canadian International Development Scholarships 2030 (BCDI 2030)', 'Government of Canada (Global Affairs Canada), administered by Colleges and Institutes Canada and Universities Canada', 'Canada', 'https://bcdi2030.ca/', 'tuition_only', 'Fully funded, but specific details on coverage (tuition, living expenses, etc.) are not provided on the main pages. It is an $80M program for 7,000+ beneficiaries.', 80000000.0, ARRAY['phd','master','bachelor']::text[], NULL, NULL, '26 Francophonie and Commonwealth countries, and other Small Island Developing States. 90% of funding goes to Sub-Saharan African countries.', 'Individuals cannot apply directly. Applications are made through partnerships between Canadian and partner country Higher Education Institutions (HEIs). At least 51% of recipients must be women. Focus on SDGs, gender equality, and employability.', NULL, 'fixed', NULL, NULL, 'Government of Canada (Global Affairs Canada), administered by Colleges and Institutes Canada and Universities Canada', 'College, technical, undergraduate, graduate, and postdoctoral programs. Custom-made training programs and research/mobility stays are also available.', '26 Francophonie and Commonwealth countries, and other Small Island Developing States. 90% of funding goes to Sub-Saharan African countries.', 'Fully funded, but specific details on coverage (tuition, living expenses, etc.) are not provided on the main pages. It is an $80M program for 7,000+ beneficiaries.', 'Not specified annually, but 7,000+ direct beneficiaries over the 8-year program (2022-2030).', 'Individuals cannot apply directly. Applications are made through partnerships between Canadian and partner country Higher Education Institutions (HEIs). At least 51% of recipients must be women. Focus on SDGs, gender equality, and employability.', 'The program has completed its two planned calls for proposals. Future calls, if any, will be announced on their website.', 'https://bcdi2030.ca/', TRUE),
